title: Farmers Deli Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Buffet, Fast food, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out
description: All vegetarian deli at the front of the Farmers Market health food store. Hot foods bar and soups start at around 10am and is 50% off after 6pm. Hot main entrees, salad bar, smoothies, fresh pressed organic juices bar, breads, desserts, and coffee. All food is either vegetarian with dairy or vegan, but no eggs. Vegans to read labels or ask.
